# FLAMeS Inference

FLAIR Lesion Analysis in Multiple Sclerosis inference pipeline.

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

```bash
flames-inference --input <input_folder_with_nifti_images> --output <output_folder>
```
